name: The City Of The Monsters
summary: The City Of The Monsters is a game where you have to arrive alive to the end of the city, you have a laser pistol to shoot your enemies and you have to avoid the bullets of your enemies moving fast across the level and hiding behind the buildings of the city, you start each level with 0 ammo and you have collect the ammo on the level, you have 8 levels on this game.
